              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM368913">Section 2(1)</extref></citation> is amended by inserting the following definitions in their appropriate alphabetical order:</text>
              <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                <def-para id="DLM2301438" quote="1">
                  <para quote="1">
                    <text><def-term id="DLM2301439">District Court</def-term>, in sections 6(2)(b)(vii), 7(b)(viii), 13(1), 14(1)(a), 15(1), 16(1), and 18(1) and (3)(b)(vii), includes a Youth Court if the suspect or respondent is subject to the Youth Court's jurisdiction</text>
